### Obtener todas las reservas
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reservas

### Obtener reserva por ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reservas/1

### Crear nueva reserva
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reservas
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "cliente": {
        "id": "1",
        "nombre": "Juan",
        "apellido": "Pérez",
        "telefono": "3512345678",
        "email": "juan.perez@email.com",
        "dni": "12345678"
    },
    "mesa": {
        "id": "1",
        "numero": 1,
        "capacidad": 4,
        "estado": "reservada"
    },
    "fecha": "2024-12-31",
    "hora": "21:00",
    "cantidadPersonas": 4,
    "estado": "confirmada"
}

### Modificar reserva (PUT)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/reservas/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "cliente": {
        "id": "1",
        "nombre": "Juan",
        "apellido": "Pérez",
        "telefono": "3512345678",
        "email": "juan.perez@email.com",
        "dni": "12345678"
    },
    "mesa": {
        "id": "2",
        "numero": 2,
        "capacidad": 2,
        "estado": "reservada"
    },
    "fecha": "2024-12-31",
    "hora": "22:00",
    "cantidadPersonas": 2,
    "estado": "confirmada"
}

### Modificar reserva (PATCH) - Cambiar estado
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/reservas/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "estado": "cancelada"
}

### Eliminar reserva
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/reservas/1
